Html:
Anyone else have a problem trying to publish KiGG in VS2008? I keep getting "Publish failed" with no other errors.

Thanks.

Nevermind... I found this http://stackoverflow.com/questions/442374/publish-failed-in-web-application-project-mvc and was able to publish successfully by just toggling "between the "Replace matching files with local copies" and "Delete all existing files prior to publish" options."
